channel.title: ~ Please help a semi-skilled coder! ~
channel.description:
Well, my problem is with a t2 error... The last couple of days i have been making new areas for mini-games ect. but have had this error a few times (in my moparscape client)
Error: T2 - 151,85,151 - 4,3240,3435 - -128,56,16,-126,
for one, i have never seen an error pop up in the consol of the moparscape cient. for 2, i have no idea why its happening and for 3, i don't even know what it means.
The error seems to happen every time i add a new global object and get anywhere near it, but i have never had any problems with it before.
~please note~ I dont get any errors while compiling.
Please help me.
